{"tid":1240790,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[以正視聽] 大律師指政府暴動說法令市民誤會，與現行法律原則及案例不符。","createTime":"2019-06-18T12:52:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-23T11:48:29.000Z","uid":37757,"like":47,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"5fedbe972d5613e1793922ce3914649c774dc0f4","tid":1240790,"uid":37757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T12:52:51.000Z","msg":"大律師：「似乎盧偉聰講緊係就只係有一種犯，就叫做主犯。佢唔會計一啲從犯或者共犯。就算無親自使用暴力，但係同其他人夥同去作出呢啲暴力既行為，都會有刑責。夥同係有兩款。<span style=\"color: red;\">第一款就係，你自己無親身使用暴力，但係你同有親身使用暴力既人有共同犯罪計畫。第二款就係，你無使用暴力既，但係你身在現場，亦都有身在現場鼓勵同埋意圖鼓勵個啲使用暴力既人。</span>這兩種都構成左暴動既參與。」<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br />\n<a href=\"http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/550847/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E5%A4%A7%E5%BE%8B%E5%B8%AB%E6%8C%87%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E6%9A%B4%E5%8B%95%E8%AA%AA%E6%B3%95%E4%BB%A4%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E8%AA%A4%E6%9C%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F550847%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25BE%258B%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%258B%2595%25E8%25AA%25AA%25E6%25B3%2595%25E4%25BB%25A4%25E5%25B8%2582%25E6%25B0%2591%25E8%25AA%25A4%25E6%259C%2583&d=qLBezvvtP0%2Ff8NIwCarvwiEyVFbloTKGHdwbQdNTMZo%3D&h=33bd7292\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F550847%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25BE%258B%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%258B%2595%25E8%25AA%25AA%25E6%25B3%2595%25E4%25BB%25A4%25E5%25B8%2582%25E6%25B0%2591%25E8%25AA%25A4%25E6%259C%2583&h=eace341c\" target=\"_blank\">http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/550847/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E5%A4%A7%E5%BE%8B%E5%B8%AB%E6%8C%87%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E6%9A%B4%E5%8B%95%E8%AA%AA%E6%B3%95%E4%BB%A4%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E